            <title>[HBASE-8039] Make HDFS replication number configurable for a column family</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8039</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To allow users to decide which column family&apos;s data is more important and which is less important by specifying a replica number instead of using the default replica number.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
